properties.areaDesc: Western Choctawhatchee Bay; Perdido Bay Area; Pensacola Bay Area including Santa Rosa Sound; Eastern Choctawhatchee Bay
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued February 5 at 7:12PM CST until February 6 at 9:00AM CST by NWS Mobile AL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest winds 18 to 23 kt with gusts up to 30 kt
expected.

* WHERE...Perdido Bay, Pensacola Bay System, Western
Choctawhatchee Bay and Eastern Choctawhatchee Bay.

* WHEN...Until 6 AM CST Friday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 AM CST THURSDAY... ...SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 6 AM CST FRIDAY
